snippet.title: Rumbleverse Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Grapital City, where everyone lives for the fight and dreams of becoming a champion. Rumbleverse is a free-to-play, 40-player Brawler Royale coming to PC, Xbox, and PlayStation in February. Visit www.rumbleverse.com to sign up for Early Access!
